{
  "texts": [
    "A 2D and 3D model was examined using the exact U-Net implementation by Fu et al.",
    "The study's findings suggest that a 3D sCT offered more accurate results with smaller MAE.",
    "In the absence of additional data, the model might use many adjacent slices to gather additional 3D context or generate independent networks for each of the three orthogonal 2D planes (230).",
    "A DL-based approach can produce images that are more realistic improve quantitative metrics.",
    "Depending on the technology, it can take from an hour to days to train a model using DL-based approaches."
  ]
}